The main entry point could be either:

1) The "urls.py" file located at /example_project/apps/todo/urls.py (if your project uses Django's standard URL configuration system for mapping URLs to views).
or 2)The "wsgi.py" or "wsgi.wsgi.whlxz" files both located in the same directory as "settings.py", which can handle WSGI application logic and settings configurations, respectively (if you have set it up that way).
